e_head__statement"><div class="_6bba37d2"><span class="a05b7640" aria-label="Statement">Reviews for the real world.</span><p data-testid="wirecutter_standard_disclosure">Wirecutter is reader-supported. When you buy through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.<!-- --> <a href="/wirecutter/about/" data-gtm-trigger="ftc_link">Learn more</a></p></div></aside><div><header class="_31c01eae bd97696c" data-scp="blog_tagline"><h2 class="ba80b2a9">Real Talk</h2> <p class="_859c2e18">Advice, staff picks, mythbusting, and more. Let us help you.</p></header><main id="main" class="ac378c15 _879c46f8" aria-live="assertive" tabindex="-1"><div class="_66fa680c"><article class="paywall"><header class="_6e91442e" tabindex="0"><figure class="b803afdf"><div class="_49bb79cb"><img src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/20200205_fakes-1024-320x160.png" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/20200205_fakes-1024-1024x512.png" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/20200205_fakes-1024-1024x512.png 1024w, https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/20200205_fakes-1024-600x300.png 600w, https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/20200205_fakes-1024-320x160.png 320w" data-sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 1024px,(min-width: 480px) 600px,320px" alt="Welcome to the Era of Fake Products" class="cb105d2e e3758800" itemProp="image" role="presentation"/><figcaption class="_5debd139"><span class="d366e790">llustration: Sarah MacReading</span></figcaption></div></figure><div class="b1f96133 blog_post__heading"><h1 class="a4feaa5e" data-e2e="post-heading" data-scp="title">Welcome to the Era of Fake Products</h1><div id="updates-box" class="_600807b5 _38762575   _190fc2df" data-scp="updates"><p class="eedaa103 _190fc2df"><time class="_38abe098 _190fc2df" dateTime="2020-02-11" data-scp="update_date"><span class="_3debadca">Published<!-- --> </span>February 11, 2020</time></p></div></div></header><div class="_1002a99b"><aside class="b2b303be"><div class="dd34110f"><ul class="fe01e0ce" data-scp="author_list"><li class="e2c45777"><img class="_33f625b8" src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/suthivarakom-ganda.jpg" alt="Ganda Suthivarakom" width="50" height="50"/><p class="d43bbc1c" data-scp="author_name">Ganda Suthivarakom</p></li></ul></div><div class="_3aa0ab3e c012dda1" data-scp="social"><p class="f1892e4e">Share this post</p><div class="_2a4b1d02" data-icon="twitter-rounded"><a class="f8ab2f92 " href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Welcome to the Era of Fake Products %7C Wirecutter&amp;url=https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/amazon-counterfeit-fake-products/&amp;via=wirecutter" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="share_twitter" rel="noopener noreferrer"><svg data-icon="twitter-rounded" class="bf2f2e97" width="35px" height="35px" viewBox="0 0 35 35" version="1.1"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-30.000000, -47.000000)"><g transform="translate(30.000000, 47.000000)"><g><rect fill="#00AEF2" x="0" y="0" width="35" height="35" rx="17.5"></rect><path d="M26,13.42125 C25.448,13.66125 24.85475,13.8255 24.23225,13.89825 C24.8675,13.52325 25.35575,12.93 25.586,12.222 C24.9905,12.5685 24.33125,12.82125 23.6315,12.9585 C23.06975,12.36825 22.27025,12 21.386,12 C19.68575,12 18.308,13.3575 18.308,15.03 C18.308,15.2685 18.33425,15.49875 18.3875,15.71925 C15.82925,15.594 13.562,14.38875 12.04475,12.555 C11.77925,13.002 11.62775,13.52325 11.62775,14.07825 C11.62775,15.12975 12.17,16.056 12.9965,16.599 C12.4925,16.584 12.01775,16.4475 11.60375,16.221 C11.60225,16.233 11.60225,16.24575 11.60225,16.25925 C11.60225,17.72775 12.6635,18.951 14.072,19.22925 C13.8125,19.29975 13.54175,19.3365 13.2605,19.3365 C13.06175,19.3365 12.869,19.31625 12.6815,19.281 C13.073,20.48475 14.20925,21.3615 15.55625,21.3855 C14.50325,22.19775 13.175,22.68225 11.7335,22.68225 C11.486,22.68225 11.24,22.